title: NFC West/AFC West Win Total Predictions, Division Odds, Futures (Football 5/15)
description:
Gambling Week on the Pick Six podcast wraps up as we dive into season win totals for the final 2 divisions. Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner-McGough to offer a 2020 outlook for teams in the NFC West and AFC West. The guys predict and prognosticate for the 49ers (8:45), Seahawks (18:15), Rams (24:45), Cardinals (31:15), Chiefs (45:30), Chargers (51:15), Raiders (58:15) and Broncos (1:06:00)
'Pick Six' is available on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Stitcher, Google Podcasts, Castbox, Bullhorn and wherever else you listen to podcasts. 
Follow the Pick Six team on Twitter: @picksixpod, @willbrinson, @seanjwagner
